The API endpoint allows you to update a specific blog by sending an HTTP PUT request to the specified URL.

### Request Body

- `title` (string): The updated title of the blog.

- `description` (string): The updated description of the blog.


### Request Headers

- `Content-Type`: application/json


### Response

Upon successful execution, the response will include the updated details of the blog, confirming the successful update.

### Response Headers

- `Status`: 200

- `Content-Type`: application/json


This API endpoint allows you to update a specific blog by sending an HTTP PUT request to the specified URL.

#### Request URL

```
{{host}}/api/blog/673f4b2aa43afc0376dbf06e

 ```

#### Request Body

- `title` (string): The updated title of the blog.

- `description` (string): The updated description of the blog.

- `tags` (array): An array of tag IDs associated with the blog.

- `categories` (array): An array of category IDs associated with the blog.


#### Request Headers

- `Content-Type`: application/json


#### Response

The response will include the updated details of the blog, confirming the successful update.

#### Response Headers

- `Status`: 200

- `Content-Type`: application/json


#### Response Body

``` json
{
    "success": true,
    "blog": {
        "id": "",
        "title": "",
        "description": "",
        "slug": "",
        "published": true,
        "publishedAt": null,
        "author": {
            "id": "",
            "name": "",
            "username": "",
            "email": ""
        },
        "tags": [
            {
                "id": "",
                "name": ""
            }
        ],
        "categories": [
            {
                "id": "",
                "name": ""
            }
        ],
        "createdAt": "",
        "updatedAt": ""
    }
}

 ```

### Request Body

- `title` (string): The updated title of the blog.

- `description` (string): The updated description of the blog.

- `tags` (array): An array of tag IDs associated with the blog.

- `categories` (array): An array of category IDs associated with the blog.


### Response

The response will include the updated details of the blog, confirming the successful update. The response body will contain:

- `success` (boolean): Indicates if the update was successful.

- `blog` (object): An object containing the updated details of the blog, including the ID, title, description, slug, publication status, publication date, author details, tag details, category details, creation date, and last update date.


